{"tid":1001344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ iPhone 出現重大私隱bug，蘋果即時停用 Group FaceTime","createTime":"2019-01-30T05:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T06:23:25.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"25cecd201de2b0e48431aa7321a1761d7a04625a","tid":1001344,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:34:41.000Z","msg":"近日，Apple iPhone 出現重大私隱漏洞，影響到用戶私隱安全。據海外多家科技媒體曝出，用戶通過 iPhone 的 Group FaceTime 功能撥打電話後，無論對方是否接聽，只要在群組功能中加入自己的號碼，就可以聽到對方手機收音咪傳來的聲音！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/354244343.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2F354244343.jpg&h=a7d8674a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前，Apple 已經展開了緊急行動，已在其伺服器禁用了 Group FaceTime，iPhone 的系統狀態匯總頁面現在顯示「Group FaceTime 暫時不可用」。據報導，該措施主要是為了迅速阻斷多人 FaceTime 在接通前就能聽到聲音的臨時解決方法，報導顯示在某些情況下，該錯誤甚至會擴展到視像通話功能。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/01/30/apple-turns-off-group-facetime-for-a-bug/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F01%2F30%2Fapple-turns-off-group-facetime-for-a-bug%2F&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfBzUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=2c345661\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/01/30/apple-turns-off-group-facetime-for-a-bug/</a>"},{"pid":"285c216f534825ef3a360e7f43a2e5cbac615512","tid":1001344,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1491755b3846c3bc2e8c3689a97c745b1a6046dc","tid":1001344,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T05:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e27db756a3dbe